window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>As a divorced single father, I live by three rules:</p> <p></p> <ol> <li>Make sure every day my daughter, Paisley, knows she’s number one in my life. No matter what.</li> <li>Keep contact with my cheating ex-wife to a minimum.</li> <li>Turn Maxwell Wineries into a legacy that keeps Paisley set for life.</li> </ol> <p>When I hire Lexi to look after my daughter, I realize I need another rule: Don’t pursue Paisley’s nanny.</p> <p>But even if I had that rule it wouldn’t matter. Because I'm breaking it already.</p>"; 
